` validates nil sandbox — returns error \"sandbox is nil\"\n32: - [ ] **3.3** Verify `StoreSandbox` validates zero ExpiresAt — returns error \"invalid expiry: ExpiresAt is zero\"\n33: - [ ] **3.4** Verify `StoreSandbox` validates empty SessionID — returns error \"session ID is required\"\n34: - [ ] **3.5** Verify ZSET scores: expiry uses `ExpiresAt.Unix()`, last activity uses `time.Now().Unix()`\n35: \n36: ---\n37: \n38: ## Phase 4: UpdateSandbox\n39: \n40: - [ ] **4.1** Verify `UpdateSandbox` uses SET with XX flag (NOT SetNX per delta-spec)\n41: - [ ] **4.2** Verify `UpdateSandbox` fails with error when key does not exist\n42: - [ ] **4.3** Verify `UpdateSandbox` does NOT modify expiry or last-activity ZSETs\n43: - [ ] **4.4** Fix implementation if using SetNX instead of SET with XX flag\n44: \n45: ---\n46: \n47: ## Phase 5: DeleteSandbox\n48: \n49: - [ ] **5.1** Verify `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` uses pipeline with DEL and ZREM (both indices)\n50: - [ ] **5.2** Verify deletion succeeds for non-existent session (DEL returns 0, ZREM returns 0)\n51: \n52: ---\n53: \n54: ## Phase 6: List Operations\n55: \n56: - [ ] **6.1** Verify `ListExpiredSandboxes` uses ZRANGEBYSCORE on `session:expiry` index\n57: - [ ] **6.2** Verify `ListInactiveSandboxes` uses ZRANGEBYSCORE on `session:last_activity` index\n58: - [ ] **6.3** Verify both list operations return `nil, nil` when limit <= 0\n59: - [ ] **6.4** Verify list operations use MGet (pipeline) to load JSON for each session ID\n60: - [ ] **6.5** Verify orphan ZSET members (session ID in index but no session key) are skipped gracefully\n61: \n62: ---\n63: \n64: ## Phase 7: UpdateSessionLastActivity\n65: \n66: - [ ] **7.1** Verify `UpdateSessionLastActivity` verifies key existence first via EXISTS\n67: - [ ] **7.2** Verify returns `ErrNotFound` when session key does not exist\n68: - [ ] **7.3** Verify uses `time.Now()` when timestamp is zero\n69: - [ ] **7.4** Verify rejects empty session ID with error\n70: - [ ] **7.5** Verify ZADD uses provided timestamp as score\n71: \n72: ---\n73: \n74: ## Phase 8: Unit Tests\n75: \n76: - [ ] **8.1** Create `pkg/store/store_redis_test.go` — unit tests with mock Redis\n77: - [ ] **8.2** Verify `go test ./pkg/store/... -v` passes\n78: \n79: ---\n80: \n81: ## Dependencies\n82: \n83: - `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9`\n84: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types`\n85: \n86: ---\n87: \n88: ## References\n89: \n90: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-013/delta-spec.md`\n91: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-012/delta-spec.md` (Store interface)\n92: - Design: `session-store/design.md`\n93: - Spec: `session-store/spec.md`\n\n(End of file - total 93 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-013 — Redis 存储实现 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/store  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Core Implementation Verification\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Verify `redisStore` struct defined in `pkg/store/store_redis.go` with fields: `cli`, `sessionPrefix`, `expiryIndexKey`, `lastActivityIndexKey`\n- [ ] **1.2** Verify constants defined: `sessionKeyPrefix = \"session:\"`, `sessionExpiryIndexKey = \"session:expiry\"`, `sessionLastActivityKey = \"session:last_activity\"`\n- [ ] **1.3** Verify `makeRedisOptions()` parses `REDIS_ADDR` and `REDIS_PASSWORD` from environment\n- [ ] **1.4** Verify `go build ./pkg/store/...` compiles successfully\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Basic Operations\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-013/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775852198101,"end":1775852198130}}}}
