{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852251370,"sessionID":"ses_286f62cb7ffeV3l1pQN8gI1KEf","part":{"id":"prt_d790a9c1e001vaBUDwzNuc0k9H","messageID":"msg_d790a85ea001P0cWpMWEkC2BSg","sessionID":"ses_286f62cb7ffeV3l1pQN8gI1KEf","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_b717747dada54e8f94dfebd4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/store  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Core Implementation Verification\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Verify `valkeyStore` struct defined in `pkg/store/store_valkey.go` with fields: `cli`, `sessionPrefix`, `expiryIndexKey`, `lastActivityIndexKey`\n- [ ] **1.2** Verify constants are accessible: `sessionKeyPrefix`, `sessionExpiryIndexKey`, `sessionLastActivityKey` (currently shared from `store_redis.go`)\n- [ ] **1.3** Verify `makeValkeyOptions()` parses environment variables: `VALKEY_ADDR`, `VALKEY_PASSWORD`, `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED`, `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE`, `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE`\n- [ ] **1.4** Verify `VALKEY_ADDR` is required — returns error if empty\n- [ ] **1.5** Verify `VALKEY_PASSWORD` is required when `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` is not \"false\"\n- [ ] **1.6** Verify `go build ./pkg/store/...` compiles successfully\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Basic Operations\n\n- [ ] **2.1** Verify `newValkeyStore()` creates client and performs PING check\n- [ ] **2.2** Verify `Ping(ctx)` executes `cli.B().Ping().Build()` and uses `cli.Do(ctx, result)`\n- [ ] **2.3** Verify `Ping` returns error on disconnected server\n- [ ] **2.4** Verify `GetSandboxBySessionID` uses GET command and returns `ErrNotFound` when key not exists\n- [ ] **2.5** Verify `GetSandboxBySessionID` handles `valkey.IsValkeyNil(resp.Error())` correctly\n- [ ] **2.6** Verify `Close()` calls `cli.Close()` and returns any error\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: StoreSandbox Atomicity\n\n- [ ] **3.1** Verify `StoreSandbox` uses `DoMulti` with: SETNX (session key), ZADD (expiry index), ZADD (last_activity index)\n- [ ] **3.2** Verify `StoreSandbox` validates nil sandbox — returns error \"sandbox is nil\"\n- [ ] **3.3** Verify `StoreSandbox` validates zero ExpiresAt — returns error \"invalid expiry: ExpiresAt is zero\"\n- [ ] **3.4** Verify `StoreSandbox` validates empty SessionID — returns error \"session ID is required\"\n- [ ] **3.5** Verify ZSET scores: expiry uses `ExpiresAt.Unix()`, last activity uses `time.Now().Unix()`\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: UpdateSandbox\n\n- [ ] **4.1** Verify `UpdateSandbox` uses SET with XX flag (not SetNX)\n- [ ] **4.2** Verify `UpdateSandbox` fails with error \"key not exists\" when key does not exist\n- [ ] **4.3** Verify `UpdateSandbox` does NOT modify expiry or last-activity ZSETs\n- [ ] **4.4** Verify error handling for `valkey.IsValkeyNil(resp.Error())` case\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: DeleteSandbox\n\n- [ ] **5.1** Verify `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` uses DoMulti with DEL and ZREM (both indices)\n- [ ] **5.2** Verify deletion succeeds for non-existent session (no error returned)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 6: List Operations\n\n- [ ] **6.1** Verify `ListExpiredSandboxes` uses ZRANGEBYSCORE on expiry index\n- [ ] **6.2** Verify `ListInactiveSandboxes` uses ZRANGEBYSCORE on last_activity index\n- [ ] **6.3** Verify both list operations return `nil, nil` when limit <= 0\n- [ ] **6.4** Verify list operations use MGET to load JSON for each session ID\n- [ ] **6.5** Verify orphan ZSET members are skipped gracefully (check for `item.IsNil()`)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 7: UpdateSessionLastActivity\n\n- [ ] **7.1** Verify `UpdateSessionLastActivity` verifies key existence first via EXISTS\n- [ ] **7.2** Verify returns `ErrNotFound` when session key does not exist\n- [ ] **7.3** Verify uses `time.Now()` when timestamp is zero\n- [ ] **7.4** Verify rejects empty session ID with error \"session ID is required\"\n- [ ] **7.5** Verify ZADD uses provided timestamp as score\n\n---\n\n## Phase 8: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **8.1** Create `pkg/store/store_valkey_test.go` — unit tests with mock Valkey\n- [ ] **8.2** Verify `go test ./pkg/store/... -v` passes\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go`\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types`\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-014/delta-spec.md` (if exists)\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-012/delta-spec.md` (Store interface)\n- Design: `session-store/design.md`\n- Spec: `session-store/spec.md`\n- Redis implementation: `changes/AR-013/tasks.md` (for comparison)","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-014/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/store/store_valkey.go\">\nERROR [157:56] too many arguments in call to vs.cli.B().Zadd().Key(vs.expiryIndexKey).ScoreMember\n\thave (float64, string)\n\twant ()\nERROR [158:62] too many arguments in call to vs.cli.B().Zadd().Key(vs.lastActivityIndexKey).ScoreMember\n\thave (float64, string)\n\twant ()\nERROR [338:65] vs.cli.B().Zadd().Key(vs.lastActivityIndexKey).Score undefined (type cmds.ZaddKey has no field or method Score)\nERROR [348:9] vs.cli.Close() (no value) used as value\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go\">\nERROR [15:2] \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/watch\" imported and not used\nERROR [66:14] cannot use &metav1.Status{…} (value of type *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status) as error value in return statement: *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status does not implement error (missing method Error)\nERROR [81:9] cannot use &metav1.Status{…} (value of type *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status) as error value in return statement: *\"k8s.io/apima